title: Drop Your Kicker and Add These Guys Before Week 1 | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 294)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Kelly and Danny Heifetz have your last-minute roster moves with their "Thank Me Now" players in the San Francisco and Pittsburgh backfields and one particularly underrated wide receivers corp (02:30). Then they run through roster cutdowns in Dallas, New Orleans, Philadelphia, Cleveland, and Tampa Bay (15:00) before looking at some stash “Thank Me Later” candidates (32:45).
